"ei y/n, are you made of copper and tellurium?"
"what?"
"because you are cute!"
"I feel that this is a pick up line that you can...
body:
“ei y/n, are you made of copper and tellurium?”

“what?”

“because you are cute!”

“I feel that this is a pick up line that you can understand only knowing science, but darling, I don’t know a thing about it”

“the symbol for copper is Cu and for tellurium is Te, so if you put them together it’s cute”

Part Four of A Heart’s Need.

Bucky loved being a father, but he loved watching Steve be a father even more. Steve was the mate Bucky could only have dreamt of as a young omega. Steve was hands-on with Theo, completely involved in the baby’s development and care.
